lib/bug.c: convert printk to pr_foo()

- Coalesce formats

- "WARNING:" prefix unchanged to keep bug format.

- printk(KERN_DEFAULT not converted.

- define pr_fmt without prefix to avoid any default prefix update
  (suggested by Joe Perches).

